column19: The Tianjin Municipal Health and Wellness Commission noted on February 19, 2022 that during the epidemic outbreak and epidemic, the city and district epidemic prevention and control commands clearly issued orders prohibiting gathering activities such as dining and entertainment.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220227135740/http://www.tj.gov.cn/sy/ztzl/tjsfyyqfkzt/sjzcwj/202202/t20220219_5808539.html
column28: The Tianjin Municipal Health and Wellness Commission pointed out on February 19, 2022 that if you are in a closed, controlled or precautionary zone, please be sure to take the initiative to report to your community and cooperate with the community's preventive and control measures, and do not leave without permission, let alone go out and gather.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220227135740/http://www.tj.gov.cn/sy/ztzl/tjsfyyqfkzt/sjzcwj/202202/t20220219_5808539.html

column10: 2022-02-21, Chengmai County, Hainan Province, pointed out that from 21 onwards, schools and kindergartens at all levels in the county area of Jinjiang Town are closed, schools and kindergartens at all levels in the county area of Jinjiang Town are closed, students and staff are suspended from returning to school specific return time to be determined.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220301044251/https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing.html?ak=572be823e2f50ea759a616c060d6b9f1&backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmbd.baidu.com%2Fnewspage%2Fdata%2Flandingsuper%3Fthird%3Dbaijiahao%26baijiahao_id%3D1725816067922468158%26c_source%3Dduedge&timestamp=1646109769&signature=8def470f9f6de03d0993431b39abdba9

column28: 2022-02-28, the Jiangxi Provincial People's Government pointed out that it had arranged for special staff to conduct a "two-code" joint check of the health code and the vaccination record of the new coronavirus for those who entered, and that those who had not received the new coronavirus vaccination had to verify the registration of their names, telephone numbers, residential addresses and other information before they could enter.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220301024213/http://www.jiangxi.gov.cn/art/2022/2/28/art_61056_3872506.html

On 2022-03-14, the Jilin Provincial Government issued a circular to ban the movement of people from the province across provinces and regions from 14 March 2022 in order to reduce the spillover and spread of the epidemic brought about by cross-provincial and cross-regional movement. If you need to go out under special circumstances, please register at the local police station and return to be isolated and controlled according to the relevant regulations on epidemic prevention and control. For those who violate the above provisions, the relevant departments will be held responsible in accordance with the law and discipline.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410133021/http://news.sohu.com/a/529962180_121106854

column25: On 2022-03-29, the Changsha Municipal Government issued a notice stating that home isolators are to live strictly alone and have no contact with family members unless necessary. If they do not live alone, they are required to live in a single room and use their own bathroom, while keeping their room door closed at all times. During home isolation, N95 masks are to be worn throughout (if you do not have a stock, please contact your community for home delivery).  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410134029/https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing.html?ak=572be823e2f50ea759a616c060d6b9f1&backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmbd.baidu.com%2Fnewspage%2Fdata%2Flandingsuper%3Fthird%3Dbaijiahao%26baijiahao_id%3D1728622354548133414%26c_source%3Dduedge&timestamp=1649598028&signature=40097750b97925f40c7c074de9ec78a1
column35: On 29 March 2022, the Shanghai Municipal Government fully implemented protest prevention subsidies and reduced housing rents for small and micro enterprises and individual entrepreneurs.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410125638/https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing.html?ak=572be823e2f50ea759a616c060d6b9f1&backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmbd.baidu.com%2Fnewspage%2Fdata%2Flandingsuper%3Fthird%3Dbaijiahao%26baijiahao_id%3D1728600596954634788%26c_source%3Dduedge&timestamp=1649595396&signature=29134d32501fb1877ebc43c1e378f8b8

column30: 2022-04-09, Taiyuan City, Shanxi Province, the municipal government issued a circular, foreign entry personnel, the assignment of red code, the first entry point isolation period of 14 days, the return and implementation of "7 days of centralized isolation + 7 days of home isolation" medical observation; the first entry point isolation period of 21 days, the return and implementation of 7 days of home isolation medical observation, the isolation period no abnormal decoding.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410131745/https://m.thepaper.cn/baijiahao_17432680

column16: On 2022-04-06, Shanghai Chongming District issued a notice to suspend offline services at the office lobby of the District Administrative Service Centre during the period of unified implementation of closure and control management (the unsealing time is subject to notification by the prevention and control department) in accordance with the requirements of the epidemic prevention and control work.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410130018/https://www.shcm.gov.cn/ztzl/009004/009004001/20220406/45bfac2a-8ff3-403b-be52-460ba4c1aea5.html

column19: On 2022-04-09, the municipal government of Chengde, Hebei Province, issued a notice that people returning to Chengde should fill in the "Chengde landing code" truthfully, take the initiative to cooperate with the registration of information, check the health code and travel code and other epidemic prevention measures, and take two more nucleic acid tests on the third day and seven days respectively, and refrain from going out until the results are available, and strictly forbid to enter or leave the gathering place.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410131016/http://www.hebei.gov.cn/hebei/15067610/15068061/15069930/index.html
column22: On 2022-04-08, the Nanjing Municipal Government issued a circular prohibiting crew members of ships with a history of travel to medium and high risk areas from boarding and disembarking. Those who need to go ashore due to special circumstances such as medical treatment of injuries should be approved by the local health department or the epidemic prevention and control command.  https://web.archive.org/web/20220410133455/https://www.jiangsu.gov.cn/art/2022/4/8/art_83410_9986569.html

column10: On 2022-04-09, the Tianjin Municipal Government issued a circular to strictly control the departure of teachers and students from school. The city implements closed campus management, school teachers and students do not leave Tianjin unless necessary, and do not teach offline unless necessary. For staff, students and outsourced service personnel who do have to leave Tianjin due to family visits and homecoming, etc., they should strictly implement measures to prevent and control the epidemic away from Tianjin, and report to the school before leaving, and provide proof of negative 48-hour nucleic acid tests and health code green codes.  https://web.archive.org/web/20211206143410/https://www.tj.gov.cn/sy/ztzl/tjsfyyqfkzt/sjzcwj/cxzc/202110/t20211020_5657683.html
